<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> brief
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol
                            <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> und <expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan> ewch
                                <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz wir <app>
<note><q type="date"><expan>am<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>nehstv<ex>er</ex>gangen</expan> sunntag fru</q>12.11.1419</note>
</app> beiden fürsten <expan>üb<ex>er</ex></expan> ir brief schriftlich
                        geantwurt und ewch <expan>ders<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>br<ex>ief</ex></expan>
<expan>abschr<ex>ift</ex></expan> in <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan> brief
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>slossen</expan> bey
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> dem Göldlein alsbald gesant
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, daz wir niht
                            <expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan> westen, er sölt <app>
<note><q type="date"><expan>am<ex>m</ex></expan> sunntag zu abend</q>18.11.1419</note>
</app><add>da mit</add> zu ewch <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> sein und des
                        morgens <add><expan>dies<ex>elb</ex></expan></add>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, <expan>burggr<ex>af</ex></expan>
<expan>Joh<ex>an</ex></expan>, fürbas bracht <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n,</expan>
                        ob er in zu <expan>Bamb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> niht
                            <expan>gefunde<ex>n</ex></expan> hett. Also
                            <expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan> wir ewch
                            <expan>ders<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> antwurt <add>aber</add> zwo
                                <expan>abschr<ex>ift</ex></expan>
<expan>hierinn<ex>en</ex></expan> verslossen, daz ir ewch dest bas darnach
                        wisset zu richten. Wir schiken ewch auch <expan>derselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> antwurt <expan>ein<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>sigelten</expan> brief an <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, <expan>burggr<ex>af</ex></expan>
<expan>Joh<ex>an</ex></expan>, auf das ob es dem Göldlein
                                <expan>missgange<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan>, daz ewch dewht, daz <add>dem
                                    <expan>burggr<ex>afen</ex></expan></add> die vorder
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> antwurt niht
                            <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan>
<expan>word<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz ir denn bestellet, daz im der brief
                                <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
<expan>w<ex>er</ex>de</expan>. Auch tun wir ewch zu
                            <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan> Truchsess und <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan> von Aufsess <expan>newlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        bey uns für und <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>geritte<ex>n</ex></expan> sind zu <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>czog</expan>
<expan>Johanns<ex>en</ex></expan>; sie <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> von den dingen nichts mit uns noch wir mit in
                        geredt, daz ir ewch darauf niht bedurft <expan>v<ex>er</ex>lassen</expan>,
                        denn den <expan>sache<ex>n</ex></expan> nachgeen in dem
                                <expan>beste<ex>n</ex></expan> form, als ir von uns gefertigt seyt,
                        des wir an ewch niht zweifeln, ir tut es <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>s<ex>ub</ex></expan> sigillo <expan>m<ex>a</ex>g<ex>ist</ex>ri
                                civiu<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> iii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan> Martini.</ab>
